.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Movie-Genre: musical, epic, sports, adventure, drama
Cigar: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
Birthday: august, april, october, may, june
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Movie-Genre:musical == Color:red
2. Movie-Genre:epic == Pet:dog
3. Birthday:august == Color:green
4. Movie-Genre:sports == Birthday:april
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Cigar:old-gold == Pet:snails
7. Cigar:kools == Color:yellow
8. Birthday:october is in the middle
9. Movie-Genre:adventure is on the far left
10. Cigar:chesterfields is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Cigar:kools is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Cigar:lucky-strike == Birthday:may
13. Movie-Genre:drama == Cigar:parliaments
14. Movie-Genre:adventure is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
